name: Itty Bitty
description: Itty Bitty is the tiniest meme coin on Solana, created to embrace the power of being small in a big world. It’s not about serious utility—it’s about laughter, vibes, and tiny wins with huge potential. From his ridiculously small hands to his massive ambition, Itty Bitty has charmed his way into the hearts of degens. The project thrives on fun, social engagement, and creative storytelling, with a clear meme identity that fuels its organic growth. Itty Bitty is here to prove that even the smallest tokens can dream big.
